Name: Steak Margherita
AttributesDescription: Increases Resonance Liberation DMG Bonus of all Resonators in the team by 40% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A massive, freshly cooked steak perfect for a family gathering. According to a well-meaning local, the only proper way to enjoy Steak Margherita is medium-rare. Noted. But let's go with medium-well, just to be safe.
